OL,11,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FIn Blackpool, Paul and entertainer
OL,13,     FVictoria are keen to extol the
OL,14,     Fvirtues of the seaside town, via
OL,15,     Fthe mediums of bingo and karaoke.
OL,16,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,17,     FThe week's final visit is to Simon
OL,18,     Fand Lana's lodges in Yorkshire,
OL,19,     Fwhere the hosts pride themselves
OL,20,     Fon luxury. But one guest compares
OL,21,     Fthe place to a caravan park...
